---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout title="Nossas Turmas - Oficina Curumim">
    <Header />
    <main class="bg-white">
        {/* Hero Section with Image Background */}
        <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-[#2ccdff] to-[#32bf6e] py-32 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-900/40"></div>
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-6 drop-shadow-lg">Nossas Turmas</h1>
                <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/95 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed drop-shadow">
                    Da oralidade, despertar dos sentidos, desenvolvimento motor, compreensão individual e do coletivo, aprendizagem da fala, leitura e escrita. As fases das crianças mudam rapidamente, por isso cada turma é dividida para explorar ao máximo o potencial de cada etapa de seus filhos, sempre respeitando o tempo individual de desenvolvimento de cada criança.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        {/* Turma 0 - Image Left */}
        <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-yellow-50">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                    <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
                        <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-400 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                            {/* Placeholder - replace with actual image */}
                            <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500/20 text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black">
                                TATUZINHOS
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-xl border-4 border-[#fbcd00]">
                            <h2 class="mb-4 text-[#fbcd00]">
                                <span class="block text-xl font-bold opacity-90 mb-1">TURMA 0</span>
                                <span class="block text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black">TATUZINHOS</span>
                            </h2>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-6">
                                <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-[#fbcd00]/10 text-[#ed8300] font-bold rounded-full text-sm">
                                    Módulo 1: 6-18 meses (aprox.)
                                </span>
                                <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-[#fbcd00]/10 text-[#ed8300] font-bold rounded-full text-sm">
                                    Módulo 2: 19-30 meses (aprox.)
                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                                Propostas envolvendo a oralidade, músicas, contação e leitura de histórias, esquema corporal, brincadeiras, sons e diferentes estímulos (visual, tátil, auditivo, motor).
                            </p>
                            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#fbcd00] to-[#ed8300] text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform shadow-lg">
                                Inscreva-se
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        {/* Turma 1 - Image Right */}
        <section class="py-20 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                    <div>
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-xl border-4 border-[#32bf6e]">
                            <h2 class="mb-4 text-[#32bf6e]">
                                <span class="block text-xl font-bold opacity-90 mb-1">TURMA 1</span>
                                <span class="block text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black">ONCINHAS</span>
                            </h2>
                            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#32bf6e]/10 text-[#32bf6e] font-bold rounded-full text-sm mb-6">
                                de 2,5 a 4 anos (aprox.)
                            </span>
                            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                                Propostas envolvendo a oralidade, músicas, contação e leitura de histórias, esquema corporal, brincadeiras brasileiras e estímulo para falar português.
                            </p>
                            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#32bf6e] to-[#2ccdff] text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform shadow-lg">
                                Inscreva-se
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-400 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                            <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500/20 text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black">
                                ONCINHAS
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        {/* Turma 2 - Image Left */}
        <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 to-orange-50">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                    <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
                        <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-400 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                            <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500/20 text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black">
                                MACAQUINHOS
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-xl border-4 border-[#ed8300]">
                            <h2 class="mb-4 text-[#ed8300]">
                                <span class="block text-xl font-bold opacity-90 mb-1">TURMA 2</span>
                                <span class="block text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black">MACAQUINHOS</span>
                            </h2>
                            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#ed8300]/10 text-[#ed8300] font-bold rounded-full text-sm mb-6">
                                de 4 a 6 anos (aprox.)
                            </span>
                            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                                Propostas envolvendo a introdução de práticas de leitura e escrita, músicas, parlendas, contação e leitura de histórias, esquema corporal, rimas, jogos, dramatizações, brincadeiras brasileiras, leitura de imagens.
                            </p>
                            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ed8300] to-[#ea1f4b] text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform shadow-lg">
                                Inscreva-se
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        {/* Turma 3 - Image Right */}
        <section class="py-20 bg-white">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                    <div>
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-xl border-4 border-[#8a00aa]">
                            <h2 class="mb-4 text-[#8a00aa]">
                                <span class="block text-xl font-bold opacity-90 mb-1">TURMA 3</span>
                                <span class="block text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black">INDIOZINHOS</span>
                            </h2>
                            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#8a00aa]/10 text-[#8a00aa] font-bold rounded-full text-sm mb-6">
                                de 6 a 8 anos (aprox.)
                            </span>
                            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                                Propostas que aproximam a criança da leitura e escrita, através da música, pequenos textos, contação e leitura de histórias, jogos, brincadeiras, dramatizações, leitura de imagens, produção de pequenos textos escritos.
                            </p>
                            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8a00aa] to-[#ea1f4b] text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform shadow-lg">
                                Inscreva-se
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-400 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                            <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500/20 text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black">
                                INDIOZINHOS
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        {/* Turma 4 - Image Left */}
        <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                    <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
                        <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-gray-400 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                            <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-500/20 text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black">
                                TUCANOS
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-xl border-4 border-[#ea1f4b]">
                            <h2 class="mb-4 text-[#ea1f4b]">
                                <span class="block text-xl font-bold opacity-90 mb-1">TURMA 4</span>
                                <span class="block text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black">TUCANOS</span>
                            </h2>
                            <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-[#ea1f4b]/10 text-[#ea1f4b] font-bold rounded-full text-sm mb-6">
                                de 8 a 12 anos (aprox.)
                            </span>
                            <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                                Propostas envolvendo a compreensão da estrutura e o funcionamento básico da língua, utilizando-as em situações de comunicação oral, de leitura e de escrita. Produção formal da língua, através de músicas, contação e leitura de histórias, bingos, caça-palavras, cruzadinhas, leitura de imagens e produção de textos escritos.
                            </p>
                            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#ea1f4b] to-[#8a00aa] text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:scale-105 transition-transform shadow-lg">
                                Inscreva-se
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        {/* CTA Section */}
        <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#2ccdff] via-[#32bf6e] to-[#fbcd00] relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/10"></div>
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative z-10">
                <p class="text-2xl text-white/90 mb-4 font-semibold">- Vem pra Oficina -</p>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-8 drop-shadow-lg">
                    Cadastre seu Curumim hoje mesmo!
                </h2>
                <a href="/contact" class="inline-block px-12 py-5 bg-white text-[#32bf6e] font-black text-xl rounded-full hover:scale-110 transition-transform shadow-2xl">
                    Entre em contato
                </a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
